version_description: This version is easier to play for beginners, because this version has no bar chords
My tab is more accurate than the others, chord placement is on point and lyrics are correct.
this song is in the key of D

This is one of my favourite songs from the new 'Youngblood' album by 5 Seconds of Summer. This is my second tab, and I hope you like it. Please feel free to correct any chords that are wrong. No capo. I'm not sure what the strumming pattern is but use whatever strumming pattern you are comfortable with.
Based on the live version: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sfsZ93T_-qE will update when studio version is released.
Most of the version is different to mine since I have an acoustic type of chords that I thought suited the song better.
